{"prompt": "Generate a website for a AI startup. The website should be innovative and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>InnovateAI</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            background-color: #f4f4f4;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d32f2f 0%, #b71c1c 100%);\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            min-height: 70vh;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        .hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: url('data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 1440 320\"><path fill=\"%23ffffff\" fill-opacity=\"0.1\" d=\"M0,192L48,192C96,192,192,192,288,192L384,192C480,192,576,192,672,192L768,192C864,192,960,192,1056,192L1152,192C1248,192,1344,192,1440,192L1440,320L1392,320C1344,320,1248,320,1152,320C1056,320,960,320,864,320L768,320C672,320,576,320,480,320L384,320C288,320,192,320,96,320C48,320,0,320,0,320Z\"></path></svg>');\n            background-size: cover;\n            background-position: center bottom;\n            opacity: 0.5;\n            z-index: 0;\n        }\n\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 4em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            color: #d32f2f;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid #fff;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #d32f2f;\n            color: #fff;\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n        }\n\n        .features {\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            background-color: #fff;\n        }\n\n        .features h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 50px;\n            color: #d32f2f;\n        }\n\n        .feature-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: #f9f9f9;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border-top: 5px solid #d32f2f;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            color: #d32f2f;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n\n        .gradient-separator {\n            height: 10px;\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #d32f2f 0%, #f44336 100%);\n        }\n\n        .about {\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            background-color: #e0e0e0;\n        }\n\n        .about h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 50px;\n            color: #d32f2f;\n        }\n\n        .about-content {\n            max-width: 900px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n        }\n\n        .about-content p {\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: #212121;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 20px;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 3em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1.2em;\n            }\n            .features h2, .about h2 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 480px) {\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1.1em;\n            }\n            .cta-button {\n                padding: 12px 25px;\n                font-size: 1.1em;\n            }\n            .features h2, .about h2 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n            .feature-grid {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>InnovateAI</h1>\n        <p>Transforming the future with intelligent solutions. We build AI that empowers businesses and inspires progress.</p>\n        <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Get Started Today</a>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"features\">\n        <h2>Our Core Technologies</h2>\n        <div class=\"feature-grid\">\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Machine Learning</h3>\n                <p>Leveraging cutting-edge algorithms to provide predictive insights and automate complex processes.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Natural Language Processing</h3>\n                <p>Enabling seamless human-computer interaction through sophisticated language understanding.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Computer Vision</h3>\n                <p>Empowering systems to see and interpret the world with advanced image and video analysis.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Data Analytics</h3>\n                <p>Extracting actionable intelligence from vast datasets to drive informed decision-making.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"gradient-separator\"></div>\n\n    <section class=\"about\">\n        <h2>About InnovateAI</h2>\n        <div class=\"about-content\">\n            <p>At InnovateAI, we are passionate about the power of artificial intelligence to solve real-world problems. Our team of experts is dedicated to developing robust, scalable, and ethical AI solutions that drive innovation across industries.</p>\n            <p>We believe in a collaborative approach, working closely with our clients to understand their unique challenges and craft tailor-made AI strategies that deliver tangible results.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 InnovateAI. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p id=\"contact\">Contact us at: <a href=\"mailto:info@innovateai.com\" style=\"color: #ff8a80;\">info@innovateai.com</a></p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Basic scroll animation for features (optional enhancement)\n        const featureItems = document.querySelectorAll('.feature-item');\n\n        const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {\n            entries.forEach(entry => {\n                if (entry.isIntersecting) {\n                    entry.target.style.animation = 'fadeInUp 0.8s ease forwards';\n                }\n            });\n        }, {\n            threshold: 0.2\n        });\n\n        featureItems.forEach(item => {\n            item.style.opacity = '0'; // Initially hide items\n            observer.observe(item);\n        });\n    </script>\n    <style>\n        @keyframes fadeInUp {\n            from {\n                opacity: 0;\n                transform: translateY(20px);\n            }\n            to {\n                opacity: 1;\n                transform: translateY(0);\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n\n</body>\n</html>"}